In the mysterious, RPG dungeon-like Tower, Confucius Kim lives a mundane existence, envying all the star hunters. One day, his wish for more is granted with a legendary skill to copy others abilities at the cost of his life. Before he can make sense of it, hes killed by the #1 hunter, the Flame Emperor! But this activates his skill and now hes copied a new one, the ability to travel back in time upon death. How will Confucius use these skills to outplay the competition and rise to the top?
(Source: Tapas)

As a powerful 8th class mage, Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar, a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness, Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic, Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy, Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time, hell get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!
(Source: Tapas)
